In the lives of most
individuals perhaps one

00:55:03.080 --> 00:55:05.830
of the most important
questions is

00:55:05.830 --> 00:55:08.020
the question of who to marry.

00:55:08.020 --> 00:55:11.080
And now instead of
going to the priest

00:55:11.080 --> 00:55:14.690
and asking, Father, who should
I marry, or going to my parents,

00:55:14.690 --> 00:55:16.760
or trying to connect
to my feelings,

