But you give it too much weight.

00:56:52.110 --> 00:56:54.520
In my calculations,
which are based

00:56:54.520 --> 00:56:56.940
on these enormous
statistical databases,

00:56:56.940 --> 00:57:01.320
I know that beauty
counts for 9.62%

00:57:01.320 --> 00:57:03.300
of the success of
a relationship.

00:57:03.300 --> 00:57:07.230
But your old-fashioned
biochemical algorithms,

00:57:07.230 --> 00:57:10.300
because of things that happened
in the African Savanna,

00:57:10.300 --> 00:57:15.060
give this data,
beauty, they give it

00:57:15.060 --> 00:57:18.400
27.5%, which is far too high.

00:57:18.400 --> 00:57:21.300
So believe me, even
though you feel

00:57:21.300 --> 00:57:24.540
that B is the right
answer, go for A.

