And this is an
empirical question.

00:57:26.600 --> 00:57:30.050
If enough people enough
times will consult and get

00:57:30.050 --> 00:57:35.590
a good answer that they will
be happy with, then with time

00:57:35.590 --> 00:57:38.880
more and more decisions
about small things and about

00:57:38.880 --> 00:57:41.340
big things will be
done in such a way.

00:57:41.340 --> 00:57:44.680
Authority will shift
from the feelings,

00:57:44.680 --> 00:57:47.070
from the inner feelings
of the individuals

00:57:47.070 --> 00:57:52.070
to the wisdom of these
external algorithms.

