And the computers are so
powerful, they know everything.

00:58:15.920 --> 00:58:18.480
They can do anything,
but they don't

00:58:18.480 --> 00:58:22.270
understand the inner
spirit of humanity.

00:58:22.270 --> 00:58:24.820
They don't understand
love or whatever.

00:58:24.820 --> 00:58:28.010
And this is why humanity
wins in the end.

00:58:28.010 --> 00:58:31.040
This is a very common plot
in many of these movies

00:58:31.040 --> 00:58:33.730
because their
audience is humans.

00:58:33.730 --> 00:58:38.120
So they have to sell
this kind of fiction.

00:58:38.120 --> 00:58:39.390
Otherwise people won't buy it.

00:58:39.390 --> 00:58:40.440
People won't like it.

00:58:40.440 --> 00:58:42.260
But there is a fallacy here.

00:58:42.260 --> 00:58:45.950
And the fallacy is that why
do you think that computers

00:58:45.950 --> 00:58:48.550
or robots will not
understand the emotions,

00:58:48.550 --> 00:58:51.100
the feelings, love, whatever?

00:58:51.100 --> 00:58:55.650
It's not some otherworldly
spiritual thing.

00:58:55.650 --> 00:58:58.350
It's, at least according
to the life sciences,

00:58:58.350 --> 00:58:59.950
it's an algorithm.

00:58:59.950 --> 00:59:03.910
So why think that
a computer will not

00:59:03.910 --> 00:59:05.950
be able to understand
an algorithm?

00:59:05.950 --> 00:59:08.240
OK, it's a
biochemical algorithm.

00:59:08.240 --> 00:59:09.900
It's not an
electronic algorithm.

00:59:09.900 --> 00:59:11.630
But what's the difference?

00:59:11.630 --> 00:59:14.150
The mathematics is the same.

00:59:14.150 --> 00:59:15.935
The calculations are
basically the same.

00:59:18.640 --> 00:59:21.400
Why does it matter
how it is done?

00:59:21.400 --> 00:59:23.850
The second fallacy,
which is part of it

00:59:23.850 --> 00:59:27.480
is that most of these
movies, not all of them,

00:59:27.480 --> 00:59:29.420
but most of them
imagine it as a kind

00:59:29.420 --> 00:59:32.450
of war between
humans and computers,

00:59:32.450 --> 00:59:33.740
or humans and robots.

00:59:33.740 --> 00:59:37.810
When the far more likely
scenario, which we are already

00:59:37.810 --> 00:59:41.010
seeing now, is not
a war but a wedding.

00:59:41.010 --> 00:59:44.890
We are talking about a merger
of the two kinds of algorithms,

00:59:44.890 --> 00:59:48.460
the biochemical and the
electronic, not a struggle,

00:59:48.460 --> 00:59:52.130
or not necessarily a struggle.

00:59:52.130 --> 00:59:54.360
Now there is one
question that still

00:59:54.360 --> 00:59:57.570
hovers over this
entire discussion.

00:59:57.570 --> 01:00:01.240
And this is whether the
life sciences are right.

01:00:01.240 --> 01:00:04.920
Does life really
mean nothing more

01:00:04.920 --> 01:00:07.580
than information processing?

01:00:07.580 --> 01:00:11.520
It may seem like it when
you read the latest articles

01:00:11.520 --> 01:00:14.360
and books on the discovery
of the life sciences,

01:00:14.360 --> 01:00:18.340
but there is still one
big hole in the story.

01:00:18.340 --> 01:00:20.690
And this is the question
of consciousness,

01:00:20.690 --> 01:00:22.920
of subjective experiences.

01:00:22.920 --> 01:00:27.850
What is called in philosophy the
hard problem of consciousness.

01:00:27.850 --> 01:00:30.180
We now understand
very well, we know

01:00:30.180 --> 01:00:34.600
how to find correlations
between particular biochemical

01:00:34.600 --> 01:00:40.400
or electrochemical
patterns in the brain,

01:00:40.400 --> 01:00:43.440
and certain subjective
experiences.

01:00:43.440 --> 01:00:45.820
But we are very,
very far from being

01:00:45.820 --> 01:00:49.860
able to understand how is
it that a particular pattern

01:00:49.860 --> 01:00:52.730
of electrochemical
signals in the brain

01:00:52.730 --> 01:00:57.160
creates a subjective experience
of love, or anger, or hate,

01:00:57.160 --> 01:00:58.760
or whatever.

01:00:58.760 --> 01:01:00.620
The life sciences--
or currently most

01:01:00.620 --> 01:01:04.510
of them-- have this
dogma that, OK, we

01:01:04.510 --> 01:01:07.850
don't know how to explain
it, but in 20, or 30, or 50

01:01:07.850 --> 01:01:10.280
years with more
experiments, more knowledge

01:01:10.280 --> 01:01:13.930
we will understand how
electrochemical signals are

01:01:13.930 --> 01:01:17.980
transformed into
subjective experiences.

01:01:17.980 --> 01:01:22.590
But at present in 2015
this is just dogma.

01:01:22.590 --> 01:01:28.130
Still today we don't have a clue
how electrochemical patterns

01:01:28.130 --> 01:01:31.490
can turn into
subjective experiences.

01:01:31.490 --> 01:01:35.390
Maybe the life sciences
have got it wrong.

01:01:35.390 --> 01:01:38.340
Maybe humans and
other animals are not

01:01:38.340 --> 01:01:40.670
reducible to algorithms.

01:01:40.670 --> 01:01:43.010
This is an open question.

01:01:43.010 --> 01:01:47.170
However, in historical
terms, it's not as important

01:01:47.170 --> 01:01:51.950
as you might think because
a religion or an ideology

01:01:51.950 --> 01:01:56.420
does not have to be correct
in what it says in order

01:01:56.420 --> 01:01:58.200
to take over the world.

01:01:58.200 --> 01:02:00.400
We have many cases
previously in history

01:02:00.400 --> 01:02:02.410
when religions and
ideologies, which

01:02:02.410 --> 01:02:06.920
said what we think today to
be completely erroneous things

01:02:06.920 --> 01:02:11.560
about the world, nevertheless
managed to take it over.

01:02:11.560 --> 01:02:16.340
In scientific terms the story,
for example, that Christianity

01:02:16.340 --> 01:02:19.190
tells about the world,
how the world was created,

01:02:19.190 --> 01:02:21.980
how humans were created, how
things work in the world,

01:02:21.980 --> 01:02:23.210
it's not true.

01:02:23.210 --> 01:02:26.380
It's simply not true, at
least according to science.

01:02:26.380 --> 01:02:28.810
But this did not
prevent Christianity

01:02:28.810 --> 01:02:31.370
from taking over
most of the world.

01:02:31.370 --> 01:02:35.080
So you don't need the truth
to take over the world.

01:02:35.080 --> 01:02:38.350
Similarly with these
new data religions,

01:02:38.350 --> 01:02:42.790
maybe they are based on a
misunderstanding of life,

01:02:42.790 --> 01:02:45.290
but this will not
necessarily prevent them

01:02:45.290 --> 01:02:47.210
from taking over the world.

01:02:47.210 --> 01:02:48.044
Thank you.

