YUVAL HARARI: Which?

01:07:03.520 --> 01:07:05.280
AUDIENCE: If you
had other groups,

01:07:05.280 --> 01:07:07.160
like if you have
more men, you were

01:07:07.160 --> 01:07:09.102
more likely to win
over the other group.

01:07:09.102 --> 01:07:11.310
YUVAL HARARI: Ah, but it's
