01:10:52.920 --> 01:10:56.810
When they tell us connect to
yourself, follow your heart,

01:10:56.810 --> 01:10:58.590
and make your
decisions from there.

01:10:58.590 --> 01:11:00.290
And this is how we
build our economy,

01:11:00.290 --> 01:11:02.140
our politcs-- it's not true.

01:11:02.140 --> 01:11:04.760
But in terms of
ideology, and this

01:11:04.760 --> 01:11:07.460
is what they are selling us
and this is what many of us

01:11:07.460 --> 01:11:09.800
believe, that we go
to the supermarket

01:11:09.800 --> 01:11:12.650
and we buy whatever
