01:21:35.355 --> 01:21:39.590
that you have absolutely no
bias when I read your book.

01:21:39.590 --> 01:21:41.130
Is that really true?

01:21:41.130 --> 01:21:43.410
Do you have any
attachments [INAUDIBLE]

01:21:43.410 --> 01:21:45.860
of any nation, religion?

01:21:45.860 --> 01:21:47.715
You may skip that.

01:21:47.715 --> 01:21:50.560
YUVAL HARARI: Well, it's
a very big compliment.

01:21:50.560 --> 01:21:54.250
Maybe the highest compliment
you can give a scientist

01:21:54.250 --> 01:21:57.780
is that he or she has no bias.

01:21:57.780 --> 01:22:03.080
I tried to write the book
with as little bias as I can.

01:22:03.080 --> 01:22:05.080
I think you can read
between the lines

01:22:05.080 --> 01:22:08.230
that there are some things
I like more than others,

01:22:08.230 --> 01:22:10.670
some ideologies,
religions, and so forth

01:22:10.670 --> 01:22:12.790
that I like more than others.

01:22:12.790 --> 01:22:17.440
But I think that my
aim as a historian

01:22:17.440 --> 01:22:23.470
is above all to describe
reality, not to judge it.

01:22:23.470 --> 01:22:26.980
It's very important
afterwards to make judgments,

01:22:26.980 --> 01:22:29.930
to decide what is good, what is
bad, where we should progress.

01:22:29.930 --> 01:22:34.180
But the most basic
challenge is first of all

01:22:34.180 --> 01:22:36.230
to describe reality.

01:22:36.230 --> 01:22:41.580
And if you start with a certain
agenda then very quickly

01:22:41.580 --> 01:22:44.990
you become blind
to much of reality

01:22:44.990 --> 01:22:48.900
because one thing almost
certain about reality

01:22:48.900 --> 01:22:50.970
is that it's complex.

01:22:50.970 --> 01:22:53.050
You take any
historical development,

01:22:53.050 --> 01:22:55.760
the agricultural revolution,
the Industrial Revolution,

01:22:55.760 --> 01:22:59.320
you will always find some bad
things, and some good things,

01:22:59.320 --> 01:23:01.000
and some neutral
things about it.

01:23:01.000 --> 01:23:02.890
So if you start with
the idea of this is bad,

01:23:02.890 --> 01:23:05.109
you can't see at
least half the story.

01:23:05.109 --> 01:23:06.650
AUDIENCE: Thank you
